    <body>
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="display-3" style="background-color: turquoise; text-decoration: underline"><b>About Ethos, Inc</b><span class="cursor"></span></h1>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="segment"><b>Mission</b></p>
            <p style="font-size: 20px">&emsp;&emsp; Our mission here at Ethos Inc is twofold. Firstly, we aim to provide the best online experience and service to our customers, 
                as well as the best and latest computer hardware in the industry for the best prices. Our second mission served as the inspiration behind 
                the company’s name. Ethos Inc seeks to maintain full transparency with its customers and employees regarding its business practices, to 
                establish strong credibility with our customers through acting on our first mission, and to ensure that ethical practices are utilized in 
                the treatment of our employees and the sourcing of our products.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="segment"><b>Business</b></p>
            <p style="font-size: 20px">&emsp;&emsp; Ethos Inc is a computer hardware distribution company active in the mainland United States of America, with over 2,500 employees 
                and owning over a dozen storage facilities across the country. Its operations are based in the city of Jacksonville, Florida, where it was 
                founded in December 2022 by three college students: Charles Williams, Logan Milbrandt, and Matthew Fernandez. The main service offered by 
                Ethos Inc comes in the form of its online store, where customers can purchase computer hardware and have it shipped to them.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="segment"><b>Executives</b></p>
        </div>
